citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1045am on
11-Jan-18.
The inspector called three different phone numbers and left messages. The inspector also knocked on the door of
the home of the ranch manager several times with no answer.
Additional Inspectors
Steneroden Katie, Veterinary Medical Officer
